00:14:51,822 --> 00:14:53,222
Fight?

294
00:14:53,222 --> 00:14:54,422
Yeah.

295
00:14:54,422 --> 00:14:56,622
My Dad's got a bad temper,

296
00:14:56,622 --> 00:14:58,122
but is a push-over,

297
00:14:58,122 --> 00:15:00,879
