00:23:25,383 --> 00:23:27,904
Huh? Is that how it sounded?

456
00:23:27,904 --> 00:23:29,387
I see.

457
00:23:29,387 --> 00:23:32,804
That's how you figured out he was Genta's father.

458
00:23:32,804 --> 00:23:34,704
Yeah, because the other two

459
00:23:34,704 --> 00:23:37,104
